{"tid":229540,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Dse考生搵工指南","createTime":"2017-05-04T16:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T14:53:00.000Z","uid":103318,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0af78796301d42e256feb8415b21d5fcf91fc858","tid":229540,"uid":103318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"身為過來人開post拯救各位dse迷途仔女，廢話唔多講，下面就先列出各種呃人技倆，再講詳細:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.ENG Herbalife呢類老牌傳銷<br />\n2.XX金融、倫敦金...各種有底薪嘅金融工/internship<br />\n3.搵工網無提及公司名嘅工<br />\n4.請人嘅時候問定有無418<br />\n5.拖糧過1星期可以上勞工處<br />\n6.(承5)<span style=\"color: red;\">如果成堆人一齊俾公司拖糧記得唔好成個傻仔咁，佢話得咁多就收咁多先，要一齊企硬上勞工處搞</span><br />\n7.炒散算係比較多錢嘅工，有時間就去銀行搞張mpf強積金卡<br />\n8.俾人屈簽約記得唔好簽，即使簽咗上庭都要話簽嗰陣精神狀態不正常/不健全精神狀態</span><br />\n暫時係咁多，下面就係我嘅部份經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.傳銷撚帶你上去似office嘅工廈開催眠大會，啲騙徒會係啲&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">高層</span>&rdquo;分享經歷時候係咁講啲<span style=\"color: red;\">正面</span>野，eg 係 啱 無錯...有幾噁心得幾噁心嚟洗你腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後會俾啲&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">課程</span>&rdquo;你推銷俾你啲<span style=\"color: red;\">朋友、屋企人</span>開單，仲會好好心提你地唔好俾屋企人知同埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你係幫緊人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.旺角總會有好多健身jj，首先佢地會開門劈你jj問你<span style=\"color: red;\">夠秤</span>未，呢個時侯你扮型笑咗笑話你夠就仆街啦!而你俾人氹到上去試下玩，會先問你攞<span style=\"color: red;\">銀行卡</span>話幫你做會員，幫你碌咗錢再迫你簽約就學我咁大吵大鬧再光速離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人問先再分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41698aa7257ef706d9f1596cbf1474e412f986cc","tid":229540,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3790973de67dd792731193b8c7230834fdb2749","tid":229540,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbece3365e3dd6843ee2792f0ee08b0f0f1d771","tid":229540,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8d47f526142812c78e1782841ffa478e06e5b9","tid":229540,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"推到上毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993f6a7a2951c32768903f8911468247c2128175","tid":229540,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c565223af08f2df60f32b77c61089e1e34524b2","tid":229540,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdcf2f7ac1ec3d5bc76542e43fa0ee99e6aabca","tid":229540,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T18:48:49.000Z","msg":"有咩真係趁係到問，香港而家真係唔少黑心陷阱"},{"pid":"55f8065774c29e61e39f0ad2091d7db1c39286fa","tid":229540,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T19:39:55.000Z","msg":"大路小小 唔好怕污糟 怕辛苦 18歲第弓份工個個都係咁"},{"pid":"2bd62c5d2ef80a497a4eedd25e9c26bbc5c693f1","tid":229540,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1d4e56d5f681244e7cb053e0ca00de1e0bf2ee","tid":229540,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo